| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3916 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1e388a6a-d4f5-5f25-b329-d78aa894719d"
